languages.text: "Ко мне обратился твой подчиненный, Мариус. Он желал стать миссионером".
"One of your subordinates by the name of Marius approached me. He expressed his desire to become a missionary."

traits.locale_text: "Einer Eurer Untergebenen namens Marius kam auf mich zu. Er verlieh seinem Wunsch Ausdruck, ein Missionar zu werden."

languages.text: « L'un de vos subordonnés, le dénommé Marius, est venu me voir pour me faire part de son désir de devenir missionnaire. »
languages.original_text: "One of your subordinates by the name of Marius approached me. He expressed his desire to become a missionary."

traits.locale_text: « L'un de vos subordonnés, le dénommé Marius, est venu me voir pour me faire part de son désir de devenir missionnaire. »

languages.text: «Uno de sus subordinados, un tal Marius, acudió a mí para expresar su deseo de hacerse misionero».
languages.original_text: "One of your subordinates by the name of Marius approached me. He expressed his desire to become a missionary."

traits.locale_text: «Uno de sus subordinados, un tal Marius, acudió a mí para expresar su deseo de hacerse misionero».

languages.text: 「マリウスというお前の部下の一人が近づいてきた。彼は聖務団に入りたいという希望を表明していた」
languages.original_text: "One of your subordinates by the name of Marius approached me. He expressed his desire to become a missionary."

traits.locale_text: 「マリウスというお前の部下の一人が近づいてきた。彼は聖務団に入りたいという希望を表明していた」

languages.text: “你有个叫马吕斯的手下来找过我，他说他想当个传教士。”
languages.original_text: "One of your subordinates by the name of Marius approached me. He expressed his desire to become a missionary."

traits.locale_text: “你有个叫马吕斯的手下来找过我，他说他想当个传教士。”

languages.text: "Astlarından Marius isminde biriyle görüştüm. Misyoner olmayı arzuladığını ifade etti."
